comments: Trent Jr. (TOR) brings his hand forward towards Kuzma (WAS), and marginal contact occurs as Kuzma receives the ball on the perimeter.
Trent Jr. (TOR) cleanly dislodges the ball from Kuzma (WAS).
Poole (WAS) cleanly dislodges the ball from Brown (TOR) as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Poole (WAS) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to the Raptors.
Olynyk (TOR) is already in Kuzma's (WAS) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Kispert (WAS) jumps alongside Trent Jr.'s (TOR) path, and he absorbs the contact by collapsing his left arm to his chest.
Holmes (WAS) cleanly blocks Brown's (TOR) shot near the rim.

After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined the foul committed by Dick (TOR) met the criteria for a clear path foul.  Poole (WAS) received two free throws and the Wizards retained possession.
Dick (TOR) is moving alongside Kuzma's (WAS) path, and the contact as they come together at the same spot is marginal.
Holmes (WAS) cleanly deflects the ball away from Olynyk (TOR) as they pursue the rebound.
Brown (TOR) brings his hand down and makes contact with Avdija's (WAS) arm prior to Agbaji (TOR) making contact with the ball.
Holmes (WAS) brings his arm forward towards Brown's (TOR) front, and the contact during the drive is marginal.
Holmes (WAS) jumps alongside Brown's (TOR) path, and the marginal contact during the shot attempt occurs to Brown's slightly extended left arm.
Holmes (WAS) brings his arm slightly forward towards Brown (TOR) and marginal contact occurs as Brown moves to defend the pass during the screen.
Replay review of the foul called on Kuzma (WAS) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Kuzma makes contact with Trent Jr.'s (TOR) arm, which affects his jump shot attempt.
Dick (TOR) commits a take foul on Avdija (WAS).
Olynyk (TOR) and Kuzma (WAS) briefly engage and disengage as they pursue the rebound.
Olynyk (TOR) is already in Butler's (WAS) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Poole (WAS) contests Brown's (TOR) jump shot, and is turning away from his body as marginal contact occurs during Brown's follow-through.
